==================================================================================
	Ruby scripting language exercises
==================================================================================

To run these on your local computre please first clone/copy this dir by using this command
git clone github_dir_path

run irb and then load file which you need to run.
e.g. to run welcome file run
load("file_path/welcome.rb") or go to ruby_code then run only load("welcome.rb")


-------------------------------------------
Description of each ruby file
-------------------------------------------
============================================
welcome.rb
============================================
Program to get user name and printing user name for welcome message.
User should needed to enter his/her name.


